For all the broken combs, hairbands and edges I still love you. 

The 4hr sessions to wash, treat and braid are worth it because you are worth my energy.

You grow back  from every emotional cut, damaging hairstyle, and time I just can’t be bothered with you. 

For the times where I have forgot to moisturise your and you have let me know your thirsty, I’m sorry.

for keeping my head warm, being gravity defying and holding a style so effortlessly, I say thank you.

4a,b,c,d,x,z hair you’re amazing and don’t let any one tell you otherwise.

Felt like giving my hair a shout out, she doing a lot.  9 months ago I shaved her but here she is again, showing out! Can we all clap for our own heads of hair in whatever shape or form it’s in 🙌🏾

node.text: 😬I’m finally sharing my first ever show 📺 , and I couldn’t be prouder to be supporting iconic women with a 4 part @youtube original ‘If I Could Tell You One Thing’. I find out the single most important piece of advice from my amazing guest to apply to my life and hopefully you guys! Go ahead and watch the full trailer on my YouTube ‘patricia bright’ #linkinbio .Feat @leomieanderson @cuppymusic @mollymae @nicolacoughlan @therealeve @stefflondon @christineohuruogu @joancollinsdbe to name a few! I’m beyond proud to deliver this and I can honestly say it was one of the most transformative experiences I’ve had,  there nothing more I love than talking, learning and hearing from others, there’s always something to take away!

Working hard, or hardly working…😎

It’s ok prioritise Entertainment, Enjoyment, and the lifestyle once in awhile.
